Entry Level - Software Developer

Smoothstack Inc

- Fairfax, VA

Smoothstack—a tech talent incubator—is one of the most rapidly growing disruptive enterprises in the IT industry in the US.
We are looking for developers who want to make a career engaging in challenging projects on futuristic technology, software development, implementing software solutions, developing apps and much more within a variety of sectors such as financial, health care, energy and federal.
New college graduates are welcome to apply. We have multiple openings in and around Washington D.C. (Metro area) and no prior work experience is required. We will provide on the job training after you are hired.
Basic Qualifications
Excitement and eagerness to learn new technology
Passion for IT development and desire to gain in-depth knowledge
Bachelor’s degree or minor in any of the following: Computer Science, Engineering, Statistics, Mathematics or Economics or equivalent training or course work experience
Basic knowledge of Java, C#, .Net, Python or similar programming languages
Interest in web programming and Object-Oriented design
